# Modules

Last verified: 2026-04-18
Source of truth: yes

## Auth module
- Files: `lib/auth.ts`, `app/api/auth/*`
- Responsibility: login/register/logout/session

## Doctor discovery module
- Files: `app/api/doctors/*`, `app/(public)/doctors/*`, `app/(public)/doctor/[id]/*`
- Responsibility: search doctors + show available slots

## Booking module
- Files: `app/api/appointments/*`, `services/appointmentService.ts`
- Responsibility: create/update patient appointments

## Doctor operations module
- Files: `app/api/doctor/*`, `app/(doctor)/*`
- Responsibility: dashboard, requests/bookings handling, calendar

## Patient profile module
- Files: `app/api/me/route.ts`, `app/(patient)/profile/page.tsx`
- Responsibility: patient account + appointment history

